Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been taken by a pyramid scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You suddenly leave your apartment, and come back sucked into a bad pyramid scheme and in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly just like you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really good detergent, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Its ingredients are 100% natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and compared to commercial products, it doesn't foam up at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that getting rid of stains is related to friction and stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Come with me to an explanatory meeting once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, will surely comprehend how wonderful the merchandise is, and want to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, and if you keep increasing the number of members,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get money too, and your rank will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the structure of it, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pyramid scheme with a capital "P".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A pyramid scheme...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like even she was disgusted by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about eating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She cleaned your apartment too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point saying that to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already late today, so you'll have to go return all this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I can go return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's embarrassing, somehow, to return a thing once you've bought it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a hassle for the other person too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, somebody might buy this from me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to sell it to, and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're forgetting that you're a hikikomori, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a hikikomori can go out and sell stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go over tomorrow and return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there still something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a hikikomori,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't want to go again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with you, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.17,Note,,0,0,0,,Understand Through Manga How to Deal With Unscrupulous Marketing Schemes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of in this pyramid scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going out, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Good morning, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Today? Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Right. Well, I'll see you at that café.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm holding a big bag like this, anybody would notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone notices it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm a big halfwit who got sucked into a pyramid scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's something you want to say, speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you bastards are having a big laugh to yourselves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why am I the only one this kind of crap happens to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Sato, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you calmed down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad if I don't return this stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What other choice do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't still be thinking somebody might conveniently take it off your hands, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you thinking that as time passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,both the merchandise and the debt will somehow disappear like smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't quit now, your quota as a member will increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it does, your debt will snowball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it, Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. This happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Sato. You already recruited two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He came for "cleaning off."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "cooling off."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The cost of the items is too high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how hard it was for me to get my hands on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste my time, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll send the cancellation paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We prepared ourselves for you to protest a little more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! We act based on a sound philosophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason why I'd act like some unscrupulous broker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd definitely succeed, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was just a little too hard for a hikikomori after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, are you eating right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not "right," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainly instant foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a hikikomori who lives alone after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I thought so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An article about the dietary habits of the people with hikikomori conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared in a recently-released science magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.97,Background2,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what it says, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That the biggest cause of the hikikomori state lies in dietary habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, you can read English?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can, at least this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With only instant foods, your brain matter becomes starved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and your thought patterns become negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And the end result is becoming a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you eat a lot of instant foods too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.59,Background2,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You sometimes want to hide out at home too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And your personal relationships aren't going very well either, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with your friends at school and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause of that is also starved brain matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Sato's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. If you're his friend, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to alleviate starved brain matter is to take in a good nutritional balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat only organic vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And with meat, too, you should carefully look into whether chemical fertilizers are used in growing feed crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, carefully examine flavorings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chemicals and such are used where you wouldn't expect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you cook, using gas isn't desirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing is charcoal. Bincho or other high-grade charcoals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a big problem with doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes too much time and costs too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is actually a better way though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A better way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.88,Background2,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I slipped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's actually a rule that I'm not allowed to tell this to non-members.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you bend the rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're begging you, Class Rep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at your mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out of this, I guess. But this is a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, huh, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you'll escape from being hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea such wonderful products existed in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Mouseroad's exclusive supplements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course the ingredients are 100% natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the production process, the utmost care is taken so that no harmful chemicals are mixed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ingesting a set amount every day activates your brain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes you able to think in a positive manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, you'll be able to escape from life as a hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not allowed to sell these to anyone but members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sato, you're "cooling off" and revoking your membership.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more, I can't sell these individually;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to sell them as a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About how much does a set cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, about this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you were going to continue as a member, I could give you 20% off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.31,Background2,,0,0,0,,Hello. Welcome to Refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,20% off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sato isn't going to buy them, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to become a member, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not "cooled off" yet, and I haven't said I'm not buying them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that there are too many for one person to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just sell what you don't need to acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the condition is that that person has to become a member too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I'll buy some from Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you succeed in increasing the number of members,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you receive a processing fee too, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If all goes well, you'll not only escape from being a hikikomori,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you can also get your hands on a large income!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is truly the Japanese Dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, Class Rep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With this stuff, I'm going to grab hold of a big dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great if you can grab that dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it said that when you try to quit a pyramid scheme, there's often trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so I brought it along just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What kind of things does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, "Things to be aware of when cleaning... no, cooling off."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"When you ask for a cooling off period, the response will often be to accept this graciously."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"But after this, other products will be recommended with skillful words,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"and there are cases where, in the end,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"rather than achieving a 'cooling off,' the target is even made to buy new products."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Be sure to proceed with caution."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To go in for a "cooling off,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and have that flipped into being sold other merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure are some stupid people in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is try "cooling off" one more time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we do, with an up-front approach, it's sure to turn into the same kind of thing as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is to push things along on your own terms and not get drawn into her rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of stuff written in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How about using it as a guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me... Could I ask you to take a survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Kurokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is Sato; we met yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kobayashi's address?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I do know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who did the product presentation with the Class Rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told him I wanted to "cool off," he was happy to give me her address.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, he seemed to be the same rank as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:18.24,Background2,,0,0,0,,Pardon me... Could I ask you to take a survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a rival, so he probably wants to trip her up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:25.19,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H17455E&\pos(490.786,42.352)\3c&H3ED2FF&\bord2.269\fnSegoe\b1\frz2.598\frx2\fry10}Agricultural-Chemical-Free Vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be right around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those are "terrace houses."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? These kinds of places are called "terrace houses," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot of weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my uncle is a specialist at this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Class Rep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't treat an old classmate who came to visit like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You, with your deceiving people again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceiving? Do you have evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make bizarre false accusations, I'll sue you for slander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We only came for a "cooling off." This is your home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you tell us you don't have the cancellation paperwork here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a family restaurant nearby. Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the paperwork along shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not buying that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want to think of another method to deceive us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we leave these and sign the paperwork, we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let us in for just a little bit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse our intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have this much Mouseroad merchandise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to laugh, go ahead and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike all of you, I'm so far in I can't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't sell this merchandise somehow, by whatever means possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer have a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Class Rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign this and hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're just not compatible after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's been true since high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It's just my pet acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take him food, he'll quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds as though you've got a tiger or a lion or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm doing Mouseroad is to earn money to pay my pet's food bills!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need to know more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you curious about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we are too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That character...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Toro Toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be great if you're able to do R.M.T., won't it, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's if you're able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this person be Toro Toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs60.504\pos(640,136.135)\c&HAB729A&}Episode 18
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8B316F&\pos(656.18,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to No Future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What vast wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody will make a success of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just going to die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Blue Bird!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:40.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504\fad(570,0)\c&HD8845F&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:40.04,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCF4A22&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504\fad(570,0)}Welcome to the Blue Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
